		<div id="siteNotice"><script type='text/javascript'>if (wgNotice != '') document.writeln(wgNotice);</script></div>		<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading">Control chart</h1>
		<div id="bodyContent">
			<h3 id="siteSub">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia</h3>
			<div id="contentSub"></div>
									<div id="jump-to-nav">Jump to: <a href="#column-one">navigation</a>, <a href="#searchInput">search</a></div>			<!-- start content -->
			<p>The <b>control chart</b>, also known as the <i>Shewhart chart</i> or <i>process-behaviour chart</i>, in <a href="/wiki/Statistical_process_control" title="Statistical process control">statistical process control</a> is a tool used to determine whether a manufacturing or business <a href="/wiki/Process_(general)" title="Process (general)" class="mw-redirect">process</a> is in a state of <a href="/wiki/Statistical_control" title="Statistical control" class="mw-redirect">statistical control</a> or not.</p>
<table id="toc" class="toc" summary="Contents">
